page_0: "I have enhanced the growth serum in an attempt to speed up the process. Of course, we won't know if the experiment has been a success until the beetles are used in combat. They should imprint on the one who is holding their pod when they hatch, and instinct should make them fiercely loyal and highly territorial. However, as with any magical experiment, there is always an unpredictable element - they could turn on their master, or simply wither and die. I cannot say until I release them. 

Viridius Cam"